    "description": {
      "value": "<div class=\"rd__b  rd__b--1\"><p>Starting at 6th level, you can give yourself vitality when you cheat death or when you help someone else cheat it. You can regain hit points equal to [[/r 1d8]] + your Constitution modifier (minimum of 1 hit point) when you succeed on a death saving throw or when you stabilize a creature with @UUID[Compendium.renegados-compendium.magias.Item.3li0IRTgnmCQexK2].</p><p>Once you use this feature, you can't use it again until you finish a long rest.</p></div>",
